articles.author: Max Olson
articles.title: Top 4 same, IU slips to 10 in latest CFP rankings - ESPN
articles.description: Oregon, Ohio St., Texas and Penn St. remain the top four in the CFP rankings, with Notre Dame replacing Indiana at No. 5. No. 12 Clemson and No. 13 Alabama would be the first teams left out of the playoff.
